# Privacy Policy

**Mahjong Tractors** — Last updated: March 25, 2026

---

> **Summary:** Mahjong Tractors does not collect, store, or share any personal user data. The app requires an internet connection to function. The only data processed is related to the display of advertisements through Google AdMob.

---

## 1. Introduction

This Privacy Policy describes how the **Mahjong Tractors** application ("we", "our", or the "App") handles user information ("you" or "user"). By using the App, you agree to the practices described in this policy.

We take our users' privacy seriously and are committed to transparency about what data is or is not collected.

## 2. Internet Connection

Mahjong Tractors requires an active internet connection (WiFi or mobile data) to function. The connection is used exclusively for loading and displaying advertisements. **No personal user data is transmitted through this connection by the App.**

## 3. Data We Do NOT Collect

Mahjong Tractors **does not collect** any personal user data. Specifically, the App:

- Does not require account creation or login
- Does not collect name, email, phone number, or any personally identifiable information
- Does not access contacts, camera, microphone, location, or device files
- Does not store gameplay data on external servers
- Does not use proprietary analytics or tracking tools
- Does not share personal data with third parties for our own purposes

All game information (score, progress, settings) is stored exclusively on the user's device and is not transmitted to any server.

## 4. Third-Party Services — Google AdMob

The App displays advertisements provided by **Google AdMob**, an advertising service from Google LLC. To display relevant ads, Google AdMob may automatically collect and process certain information, including:

- Device advertising identifier (GAID on Android, IDFA on iOS)
- Device information (model, operating system, language)
- IP address (for approximate geolocation)
- Ad interaction data (clicks, impressions)

The collection and processing of this data is performed directly by Google, in accordance with the [Google Privacy Policy](https://policies.google.com/privacy) and [Google Partner Policies](https://policies.google.com/technologies/partner-sites).

Mahjong Tractors does not have access to personal data collected by Google AdMob and does not use it for any proprietary purpose.

## 5. Consent for Personalized Ads

Depending on your location and applicable data protection laws, Google AdMob may request your consent before displaying personalized ads. You can manage your ad preferences directly in your device settings:

- **Android:** Settings → Google → Ads → Opt out of Ads Personalization
- **iOS:** Settings → Privacy → Apple Advertising → Disable Personalized Ads

Even with personalization disabled, you will continue to see ads, but they will not be based on your interests.

## 6. Children's Privacy

Mahjong Tractors is not directed at children under the age of 13. We do not knowingly collect personal information from children. If you are a parent or guardian and believe your child has provided us with personal data, please contact us so we can take the necessary actions.

## 7. GDPR Compliance (European Users)

For users located in the European Economic Area (EEA), we comply with the General Data Protection Regulation (GDPR):

- The App does not directly process personal data
- Any data processed by Google AdMob follows Google's policies, with Google acting as an independent controller for ad display purposes
- You can exercise your data subject rights (access, correction, deletion, etc.) directly with Google through your [Google Account settings](https://myaccount.google.com/data-and-privacy)

## 8. Security

Since the App does not collect or store personal data on our own servers, there is no risk of personal information leakage from our service. The security of data processed by Google AdMob is Google's responsibility, which employs enterprise-level security measures.

## 9. Changes to This Policy

We may update this Privacy Policy periodically. Any changes will be posted on this page with the revised update date. We recommend reviewing this policy regularly to stay informed about how we protect your information.

